E_{inc} &amp;amp;= E_0e^{i(\omega t+\beta\sin\Omega t)} \\
&amp;amp;\approx E_0\left[J_0(\beta)e^{i\omega t}+J_1(\beta)e^{i(\omega+\Omega)t}-J_1(\beta)e^{i(\omega-\Omega)t}\right]
\end{aligned}
